@startuml
title Figura 4.1 - Máquina de estados del GameManager

hide empty description
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
  BorderColor #333333
}

[*] --> Menu

Menu --> CharacterSelection : Iniciar partida
CharacterSelection --> Playing : Clase seleccionada

Playing --> Paused : Tecla ESC
Paused --> Playing : Reanudar
Paused --> Menu : Menú principal

Playing --> GameOver : Vida del jugador ≤ 0
Playing --> Victory : bossesDefeated >= bossesToWin\n(RoomFlowController)

GameOver --> Menu : Volver al menú\n(automático tras retardo)
Victory --> Menu : Volver al menú

@enduml
